ygData.messageBody:
Heheh. Well if u need netted or woven u gotta risk going to the Swamp or the
upper Guk for it. I would suggest that u hunt the froggie fisherman. They give
netted stuff. Or if u're brave enough go into Upper Guk but I would suggest not
to cross the bridge. It really really make it hard to run. U'll drop into the
water where the froggie warrior would slaughter u. I only have one record of
making that run across the bridge with 6 froggies at my back successfully. But I
can't seems to do it again. :P
